@startuml goroutine-lifecycle
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

title Goroutine Lifecycle Management Pattern

participant "Handler" as H
participant "WaitGroup" as WG
participant "Goroutine" as G
participant "Context" as C

== Startup ==

H -> WG : Add(1)
H -> G : go func()
activate G
G -> G : defer wg.Done()
G -> C : select ctx.Done()
note right: Goroutine listens\nfor cancellation

...time passes...

== Shutdown ==

H -> C : cancel()
C --> G : ctx.Done() fires
G -> G : cleanup
G -> WG : Done()
deactivate G
H -> WG : Wait()
note right: Shutdown() blocks\nuntil goroutine exits

== Applied In ==

note over H, C
  SSE streaming handlers
  Cache invalidation loops
  Model refresh deduplication
  Debate log lifecycle tracking
  ACP graceful shutdown
end note

@enduml
